Class AccessSymbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • cetus.hir.PseudoSymbol
      • cetus.hir.AccessSymbol
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Symbol
    public class AccessSymbol
extends PseudoSymbol
implements Symbol
    AccessSymbol is intended to express an object of AccessExpression as a Symbol object. This will replace AccessSymbol if everything works fine.
